<h3 class="subtitle">This spagetti recipe is possibly the best AND easiest out there. Its meaty, cheesy, and full of flavor!</h3>

<h1 id="ingredients">Here are the ingredients you will need for this delicous pasta!</h1>
<ul>
<li>1lb ground beef</li>

<li>4 stalk celery(chopped</li>

<li>1 can diced tomatos</li>

<li>1 can tomato paste</li>

<li>1 mushroom can red wine, 5,6 cloves</li>

<li>1/4 cup chopped fresh parsley</li>

<li>1t oregano</li>

<li>1t salt</li>

<li>1 onion chopped</li>

<li>4 cloves garlic, minced</li>

<li>1 can tomato sauce 29oz</li>

<li>1 can sliced mushrooms</li>

<li>1 can beef broth (CONDENSED!)</li>

<li>2 bay leaves</li>

<li>1 t.sugar</li>

<li>fresh ground pepper</li>

<li>1 t. basil</li>



</ul>
 <ol>
<li>Brown meat, drain fat</li>
<li>Add chopped onion and celery(equal amounts of each</li>
<li>Put in minced garlic towards the end</li>
<li>Add meat, onion, and celery to stock pot with rest of ingredients, bring to a boil (cover with lid) Simmer for at least 3 hours on med/low heat </li>



<h1>Serve on a plate, and enjoy!</h1>



<h1>This was very fun to make!</h1>



 </ol>
